lis = Linux install scripts

options:

-s|--setup		Run complete setup
			Updates & upgrades system
			Installs minimal packages aka base
			Lets you choose aditinal packages to install

-i|--install [PACKAGE]	Installs a specific package

-e|--env [FUNCTION]	Runs environment functions
			[create]
			[delete] 

-r|--remove [PACKAGE]	Removes a specific packages
